What? What's wrong? If it wasn't for you, would I have gotten hurt?

126
00:09:35,850 --> 00:09:37,546
Doctor Zhan.

127
00:09:40,200 --> 00:09:42,750
Can my sister go back to Linjiang?

128
00:09:42,750 --> 00:09:45,846
Yeah, she is on the list.

129
00:09:45,846 --> 00:09:47,100
How about you?

130
00:09:47,100 --> 00:09:49,750
Are you one of the evacuees this time?

131
00:09:49,750 --> 00:09:51,506
What's wrong?

132
00:09:51,506 --> 00:09:53,500
Doctor Zhan is my sister's primary care doctor.

133
00:09:53,500 --> 00:09:56,100
She knows my sister's situation well.

134
00:09:56,100 --> 00:09:59,010
If she can go back with us, that would be great.

135
00:09:59,010 --> 00:10:00,410
Yeah.

136
00:10:01,420 --> 00:10:04,140
Okay. Then I can rest assured.

137
00:10:09,280 --> 00:10:11,504
I told you to get some rest.

138
00:10:11,504 --> 00:10:13,340
