163
00:11:32,360 --> 00:11:34,492
So hard.

164
00:11:35,840 --> 00:11:39,130
- Have you had noodles? 
 - I had it when I was waiting for you.

165
00:11:39,130 --> 00:11:42,710
It's hard to get hot water. Have it all.

166
00:11:42,710 --> 00:11:43,650
Thanks.

167
00:11:43,650 --> 00:11:46,426
You're welcome. Quickly eat.

168
