Sis, I remember when we were young,

169
00:11:48,660 --> 00:11:51,910
I made mistakes and my mom forbade me from eating anything.

170
00:11:51,910 --> 00:11:54,610
You would give me something to eat secretly. Do you remember that?

171
00:11:54,610 --> 00:11:57,270
That was a pack of cup noodles. We shared it.

172
