It was really tasty.

173
00:12:05,630 --> 00:12:08,150
Be careful. Come on.

174
00:12:08,150 --> 00:12:09,550
Here.

175
00:12:16,380 --> 00:12:18,090
 Be careful.

176
00:12:18,090 --> 00:12:20,050
 Put your feet on the bed first.

177
00:12:24,200 --> 00:12:25,792
Ms. Luo.

178
00:12:32,870 --> 00:12:34,534
How are you?

179
00:12:39,680 --> 00:12:44,120
The principal... knew you and the kids were safe.

180
00:12:44,960 --> 00:12:47,032
He died in peace.

181
00:13:19,380 --> 00:13:22,280
Get some good rest. Goodbye.

182
