I'll apologize to him now. Okay?

189
00:14:15,860 --> 00:14:19,500
Get some rest and take your medicine.

190
00:14:19,500 --> 00:14:21,340
I put the pills here.

191
00:14:41,240 --> 00:14:42,748
Xiong Fei.

192
00:14:44,500 --> 00:14:46,052
What's wrong?

193
00:14:46,052 --> 00:14:48,378
You saved my sister.

194
00:14:48,378 --> 00:14:51,006
I won't forget what you did for her.

195
00:14:51,006 --> 00:14:54,594
A reward is not the reason we go to save others.

196
00:14:54,594 --> 00:14:56,208
Thanks.

197
