She is an innocent girl.

203
00:15:18,314 --> 00:15:23,024
I don't want her to be influenced by the circumstances around her.

204
00:15:24,440 --> 00:15:26,380
Don't worry.

205
00:15:26,380 --> 00:15:29,170
I and Ms. Luo, we can say we are strangers.

206
00:15:29,170 --> 00:15:31,770
And later we won't have any connections.

207
00:15:31,770 --> 00:15:33,210
Okay.

208
00:15:35,790 --> 00:15:40,480
In the future, if you need advice or help with any legal matters,

209
00:15:40,480 --> 00:15:42,512
you can come to me.

210
00:15:58,910 --> 00:16:00,670
Come in.

211
00:16:03,840 --> 00:16:06,496
Ms. Luo, how do you feel?

212
00:16:06,496 --> 00:16:08,438
Do you feel better?

213
00:16:09,120 --> 00:16:13,611
Doctor Cai, would you mind introducing Ms. Luo's condition to us?

214
00:16:14,240 --> 00:16:17,480
Ms. Luo, they're reporters from Linjiang.

215
00:16:17,480 --> 00:16:19,120
What are you doing?

216
00:16:20,110 --> 00:16:22,046
Please get out.

217
00:16:22,046 --> 00:16:23,760
Here's the situation.

218
00:16:23,760 --> 00:16:26,861
I am a doctor at Linjiang Hospital, Cai Yuxiao.

219
00:16:26,861 --> 00:16:28,690
They are reporters from Linjiang.

220
00:16:28,690 --> 00:16:31,560
We'd like to interview your sister.

221
00:16:31,560 --> 00:16:34,660
Interview? There is no interview needed here.

222
00:16:34,660 --> 00:16:37,960
She needs to rest. Please get out.

223
00:16:37,960 --> 00:16:39,200
Don't get me wrong.

224
00:16:39,200 --> 00:16:44,210
They just want to bring some good news to the audiences who care about the Fengxi earthquake.

225
00:16:44,210 --> 00:16:46,412
Good news?

226
00:16:46,412 --> 00:16:49,310
Please stop shooting now. Turn off your camera.

227
00:16:50,390 --> 00:16:53,840
Fengxi citizens are suffering from illness or injury, and some of them even died.

228
00:16:53,840 --> 00:16:55,880
As a doctor, you don't save others,

229
00:16:55,880 --> 00:16:58,280
but are accepting an interview here to enjoy the limelight.

230
00:16:58,280 --> 00:17:00,260
Is it good news?

231
00:17:00,260 --> 00:17:01,792
Please get out.

232
00:17:02,980 --> 00:17:05,480
Okay, fine. I'll show you around outside.

233
00:17:05,480 --> 00:17:07,390
Okay. Sorry.

234
00:17:07,390 --> 00:17:08,990
Let's go.

235
00:17:12,590 --> 00:17:14,446
Are you feeling well?

236
00:17:20,140 --> 00:17:21,840
Ignore them.

237
00:17:21,840 --> 00:17:24,300
Medical assistance after the earthquake is a matter of urgency.

238
00:17:24,300 --> 00:17:27,380
You can see that we have a lot of simple operating tables on site.

239
00:17:27,380 --> 00:17:31,771
Doctor Cai, how many operations like this do you handle a day?

240
00:17:31,800 --> 00:17:35,700
I don't count that. As long as there is a need and there are patients, we will do it.

241
00:17:35,708 --> 00:17:37,440
 Thanks for your hard work.

242
00:17:37,440 --> 00:17:40,620
 It is hard work like yours that has saved so many lives.

243
00:17:40,620 --> 00:17:42,720
 What kind of faith is it that sustains you?

244
00:17:42,720 --> 00:17:45,290
 Saving others is our duty as doctors.

245
00:17:45,290 --> 00:17:48,870
In TV interviews, Dr. Cai looks so handsome.

