250
00:17:57,214 --> 00:18:03,070
Hearing him saying it in a trembling voice, saving one, and one more,

251
00:18:03,070 --> 00:18:05,874
I am so touched.

252
00:18:09,060 --> 00:18:11,640
 Team One has achieved your task so successfully.

253
00:18:11,640 --> 00:18:13,510
 Thanks for your hard work.

254
00:18:13,510 --> 00:18:19,100
 And now Team Two is there, our daily work can't run without doctors.

255
00:18:19,100 --> 00:18:24,550
Zhan Yan, please come back with the critically ill patients.

256
00:18:24,550 --> 00:18:25,820
Yes.

