260
00:18:58,820 --> 00:19:00,464
All right?

261
00:19:14,690 --> 00:19:18,990
Lele, later when I'm free, I'll visit you.

262
00:19:24,990 --> 00:19:26,390
Be good.

263
00:19:36,200 --> 00:19:38,200
Just watch out.

264
00:19:38,200 --> 00:19:39,964
 Don't fall down.

265
00:19:46,920 --> 00:19:48,190
- What? 
 - Let me.

266
00:19:48,190 --> 00:19:50,290
- Be careful. 
 - What?

267
00:19:55,790 --> 00:19:57,040
