269
00:20:02,480 --> 00:20:04,510
Hey, bro. Don't sleep.

270
00:20:04,510 --> 00:20:06,110
Please hang on.

271
00:20:06,110 --> 00:20:08,230
- Epinephrine. 
 - Okay.

272
00:20:09,170 --> 00:20:11,226
Please hang on.

